		</div>
		<div class="comment_text"><p>How will it cost you big? Yes it costs money to pay for CF. But if I can get something done in half the time, with more features, than it is worth the cost. I just don't get how people look at ONE facet of price only. It's like Windows. While I've complained about Windows, I'd rather pay the price for the OS than use Linux since Windows is easier to use.</p><p>Anyone who says the price is the ONLY concern does NOT have a full view of what 'cost' really entails.</p></div>
